---
title: Sweet Soy Prawn & Veggie Stir-Fry with Charred Corn Rice & Peanuts
description: A prawn stir-fry isn’t complete without veggies and a sticky dark sauce. Make sure it coats everything, because this stir-fry sauce is
addictive. You'll need a fluffy rice to help soak it up so nothing it left in the bowl when you’re done.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-soy-prawn-stir-fry-charred-corn-rice-8253495b.jpg
